    <li><strong>Best for text in images:</strong> Ideogram — 25 free prompts daily with stellar text rendering</li>
    <li><strong>Best for quick edits:</strong> Clipdrop — background removal, upscaling, cleanup</li>
    <li><strong>Best real-time generation:</strong> Krea — live AI image creation as you type</li>
