<h2>3. Leonardo AI — Best Free Tier for Creatives</h2>
<p><strong>Rating: 4.5/5</strong></p>
<p>Leonardo AI offers one of the most generous free tiers available: 150 credits daily, which replenish each day. This is enough for dozens of image generations, plus access to their canvas editor, AI model training, and multiple fine-tuned models for different art styles — from photorealism to pixel art and concept art.</p>
<p>Leonardo is particularly strong for game assets and character design. Its platform includes features like image-to-image generation, background removal, and an intuitive interface that rivals paid tools. For content creators on a budget, it's hard to beat.</p>
<p><strong>Best for:</strong> Game developers, concept artists, content creators<br/>
<strong>Free tier:</strong> 150 credits/day</p>
