<h2>4. Ideogram — Best for Text in Images</h2>
<p><strong>Rating: 4.4/5</strong></p>
<p>Ideogram's free tier grants 25 prompts per day, making it one of the most usable free tools for regular content creation. Its standout feature is industry-leading text rendering — achieving approximately 90% accuracy on embedded text in images. This makes it the go-to free option for creating posters, social media graphics, ads, and any image that needs legible text.</p>
<p>The Ideogram 4.0 models offer Turbo, Balanced, and Quality tiers within the free version. While the free tier has a watermark on some outputs, the text accuracy and image quality are genuinely impressive for a free tool.</p>
<p><strong>Best for:</strong> Marketers, social media creators, poster and ad design<br/>
<strong>Free tier:</strong> 25 prompts/day</p>
