<p><strong>Rating: 4.3/5</strong></p>
<p>Clipdrop by Stability AI offers a suite of AI-powered image editing tools with a limited free tier. It excels at practical tasks: background removal, image upscaling, relighting, cleanup, and text-to-image generation. The interface is fast and intuitive — upload an image and get results in seconds.</p>
<p>The free tier has usage limits but is generous enough for occasional use. For anyone who needs quick edits without launching a full photo editor, Clipdrop is a top free option available.</p>
